title: Max Bradshaw: Zombie Invasion v1.03 Android
description:
Meet Max Bradshaw, intrepid adventurer and all around hero. Then help him save the world from a zombie invasion in this modern action adventure game designed to bring back some of those classic gaming feelings.
Battle zombies with intuitive touch screen controls!
Drive cars!
Blow things up with tanks!
Fly helicopters!
Rescue scientists!
Save the world!
Are you Max enough?

What's in this version : (Updated : Jan 6, 2016)
Improved driving responsiveness.
Required Android O/S : 2.3+
